name: Master Renovators
overview: Master Renovators is supplying its services of renovating kitchen and bathrooms in Melbourne from 40 years. With this much of experience, it is needless to say that the brand is extraordinarily specializes in its filed. Master Renovators is headed by the HIA award winning builder Charles Brincat. They provide a comprehensive solution for bathroom and kitchen renovation throughout the Melbourne and its suburbs areas. Starting from design to installation, they do it all. With renovation Masters is also into interior decoration. The level of interior decoration provided under its banner has been awarded by the testimonials and loyalty of customers who availed their services.
